Privacy Policy
Zee Palm, LLC ("Zee Palm," "we," "us," or "our") takes your privacy seriously. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and disclose personal information in connection with our efforts to generate leads.
Information Collection and Use
We may collect personal information from you when you fill out a form on our website, contact us by phone or email, or interact with us on social media. This may include your name, email address, phone number, company name, and any other information you provide.
We use this information to contact you with marketing and promotional materials about our products and services, to respond to your inquiries, and to improve our website and user experience.
Sharing Your Information
We will not share your personal information with any third-party companies without your consent, except as required by law or as necessary to fulfill your requests.
Your Choices
You may opt-out of receiving marketing and promotional materials from us at any time by clicking the "Unsubscribe" link in the emails we send you or by contacting us directly at contact@zeepalm.com.
Security
We take reasonable precautions to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no data transmission over the Internet can be guaranteed to be 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee the security of your information.
Changes to This Policy
We reserve the right to modify or update this privacy policy at any time. If we make material changes to this policy, we will notify you by email or by posting a notice on our website.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how we use your personal information, please contact us at
contact@zeepalm.com
or
